dct_title_s: Map showing the location of lands in the Town of Harrison, Hudson County, N.J.
dct_description_sm: Map showing the location of lands in the town of Harrison, Hudson County, N.J. for the title to which the Town of Harrison makes application to the Riparian Commissioners. Map covers area from Sussex Street to Cumberland Street in the town of Harrison. Map shows a layout of the town of Harrison and includes the Passaic River.
